Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with interval temporal logic and reactive synthesis. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also likely as the paper focuses on the synthesis of controllers. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possible category as the paper discusses the use of soft requirements in guiding controller synthesis. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with the synthesis of efficient runtime enforcement shields. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper discusses the use of soft requirements in improving the latency of controlled systems.
